  "lyrics": "🎵 🎵Everyday I hear the radio🎵 🎵Telling me to go past the line🎵 🎵I know you're not a nighting🎵 🎵I know it's right🎵 🎵Feel the winds in every way🎵 🎵In the race in overpay🎵 🎵Got money spending dollars on a day🎵 🎵Do you know it's just a vacay?🎵 🎵I don't know but you want that so🎵 🎵Now I know and you feel it all🎵 🎵You feel it all🎵 🎵Lost in the times that keep changing🎵 🎵Want this to make it more than it seems🎵 🎵To be in the dark🎵 🎵You know I'm just like, baby can you feel it?🎵 🎵Can you feel it?🎵 🎵The moment that it's real🎵 🎵Is it really you?🎵 🎵Curtain dropped over mine🎵 🎵Curtain dropped over time🎵 🎵Curtain black was all we kept🎵 🎵The sound of lying that you hear🎵 🎵It's just a sign that you fear🎵 🎵It's just the, the only thing that makes you here🎵 🎵When silence, through everything that left you🎵 🎵Lost everything that is dear to you🎵 🎵Love🎵 🎵Die, die🎵 🎵Love, love, love🎵 🎵Times that made me all upset🎵 🎵And every single laugh🎵 🎵You triggered with your embers🎵 🎵The embers of my righteous daughter🎵 🎵It's my disaster🎵 🎵How can you take away my last hour?🎵 🎵It's my disaster🎵 🎵How do you make it?🎵 🎵Nothing but vaguelines🎵 🎵That we crossed🎵 🎵It just was the moment that we lost🎵 🎵Your hand🎵 🎵Your face🎵 🎵I need the best for each day🎵 🎵Invested in seed🎵 🎵I was just fetal, just complicated🎵 🎵Repeated🎵 🎵Hated🎵 🎵Denied🎵 🎵Exasperated🎵 🎵Nuclear war🎵 🎵Nuclear war🎵 🎵Anything in the galaxy🎵 🎵I might think I need to get my cranium checked🎵",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 9.020000457763672,
      "text": "🎵",
      "start": 8.0600004196167
    },
    {
      "end": 16.559999465942383,
      "text": "🎵Everyday I hear the radio🎵",
      "start": 14.300000190734863
    },
    {
      "end": 20.139999389648438,
      "text": "🎵Telling me to go past the line🎵",
      "start": 17.219999313354492
    },
    {
      "end": 24.399999618530273,
      "text": "🎵I know you're not a nighting🎵",
      "start": 20.920000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 27.459999084472656,
      "text": "🎵I know it's right🎵",
      "start": 24.399999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 31.459999084472656,
      "text": "🎵Feel the winds in every way🎵",
      "start": 28.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 34.7400016784668,
      "text": "🎵In the race in overpay🎵",
      "start": 31.459999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 38,
      "text": "🎵Got money spending dollars on a day🎵",
      "start": 34.7400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 41.18000030517578,
      "text": "🎵Do you know it's just a vacay?🎵",
      "start": 38
    },
    {
      "end": 45.41999816894531,
      "text": "🎵I don't know but you want that so🎵",
      "start": 41.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 49.880001068115234,
      "text": "🎵Now I know and you feel it all🎵",
      "start": 45.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 53.540000915527344,
      "text": "🎵You feel it all🎵",
      "start": 49.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 58.18000030517578,
      "text": "🎵Lost in the times that keep changing🎵",
      "start": 54.900001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 63.720001220703125,
      "text": "🎵Want this to make it more than it seems🎵",
      "start": 59.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 67.31999969482422,
      "text": "🎵To be in the dark🎵",
      "start": 64.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 71.12000274658203,
      "text": "🎵You know I'm just like, baby can you feel it?🎵",
      "start": 67.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 71.80000305175781,
      "text": "🎵Can you feel it?🎵",
      "start": 71.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 73.68000030517578,
      "text": "🎵The moment that it's real🎵",
      "start": 71.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 74.95999908447266,
      "text": "🎵Is it really you?🎵",
      "start": 73.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 76.86000061035156,
      "text": "🎵Curtain dropped over mine🎵",
      "start": 74.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 78.31999969482422,
      "text": "🎵Curtain dropped over time🎵",
      "start": 76.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 80.87999725341797,
      "text": "🎵Curtain black was all we kept🎵",
      "start": 78.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 84.45999908447266,
      "text": "🎵The sound of lying that you hear🎵",
      "start": 80.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 87.9000015258789,
      "text": "🎵It's just a sign that you fear🎵",
      "start": 84.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 93.55999755859375,
      "text": "🎵It's just the, the only thing that makes you here🎵",
      "start": 87.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 98.58000183105469,
      "text": "🎵When silence, through everything that left you🎵",
      "start": 93.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 103.76000213623047,
      "text": "🎵Lost everything that is dear to you🎵",
      "start": 98.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 106.13999938964844,
      "text": "🎵Love🎵",
